<plot>Romantic-comedy with a sort of drama based on the story of a Latin womanizer Carlos (Sonny Parmar) who meets Annie (Kelly Cohen), she finally seems to be the woman of his life. He is having a solid relationship with her but suddenly his ex-girlfriend Barbara (Aimeé Steele) appears in his life. This film will explore how a past relationship can endanger your actual love life if you decide to have an affair with your past.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?569900</url></doc>
